text: The Ataris are an American punk rock band from Anderson, Indiana. == Musical style and influences == The Ataris' music has been described as alternative rock, emo, indie rock, pop punk and punk rock. == References == == Other websites == * Category:Musical groups established in 1995 Category:Alternative rock bands Category:American punk bands Category:Emo bands Category:Indie rock bands Category:Pop punk bands
